_sText:
This map can have up to 34 players which is a lot for a this map, it's best to play with around 0 - 24 players really, but you can try with a full amount, although don't expect it to run as smooth!:) 

Hope you give feedback! I'm going to post a numerous amount of maps! 

If you are to download this map, and are thinking of adding it to a server, please contact me and tell me what the servers IP is, love to come see it on a server!

To download this map, place into your 'maps' folder in 'cstrike' if you don't know how, google or use youtube to find out! How I found out!
